name: Hail us.!
description:
It's about what me and my lil' brother been through together. We chose the path we think it's right for us, i let him sit on the first row and i'm the captain.
Yeah..siblings fight a lot, and it's a kind of love still, we posess each other. For all the siblings out there, slide that line you want and say it out loud "Hail, us.!". Yes, Hail us
